# App

Welcome to My App! 
This is a login screen and registration form built using Jetpack Compose.

## Features

1.Login functionality with email and password inputs
2.Registration form for new users
3.Validation for empty fields
4. Material theming and styling

## Installation

To use this project, follow these steps:
1. Clone the repository: `git clone `
2. Open the project in Android Studio or your preferred IDE.
3. Build and run the app on an emulator or physical device.

## Usage

1. Launch the app on your device or emulator.
2. On the login screen, enter your email and password.
3. If you're a new user, click on the "New User? Click" text to access the registration form.
4. Fill in the required fields in the registration form.
5. Click the "Submit" button to register.
6. Back on the login screen, click the "Login" button to log in with your credentials.
